# Optional override for the API server the desktop client talks to.
# Precedence: Settings screen override > this env var > built-in default.
#
#   Development default : http://localhost:4000   (the running Next.js webapp)
#   Production default  : https://app.ptc-loyalty.example  (change in electron/config.ts)
#
# Example (point a dev build at a staging server):
# POS_API_BASE_URL=https://staging.ptc-loyalty.example
